      p I appreciate the music as a whole of both the musical styles and the people who keep it alive: bands, fans, cultural managers, local labels, etc; My friends would say that, after all, WE ARE THE SCENE.
      p The music has given me good times and friends just when I have needed it most and it is a place of refuge where I can develop freely and keep it if I want to get out of all external interaction, so it allows me to concentrate and rediscover myself. It has given greater impact to the day to day because choosing wisely the songs that fit with each phenomenal experience, has turned it into a necessary soundtrack to transmit my emotions and judgments about our surroundings.
